Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:06.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어지러운 전국 시대.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:06.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is the turbulent Sengoku period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:11.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리인이 사는 지팡구국에서는 군웅할거하여 밤낮으로 접전이 계속되고
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:11.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Warlords keep on fighting day and night over\NJipangu State, where Karakuri people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:16.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리 무예가들도 승리와 영광을 꿈꾸며 맹렬히 싸우고 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:16.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri Martial Artists were sharpening their swords, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:23.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고 지금, 카라쿠리 무예가 제일을 꿈꾸는 터무니없는 영웅이 탄생했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:23.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, seeking to be the number one Karakuri Martial Artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 등장이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:26.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:33.17,TitleOP,ko,0,0,40,,카라쿠리 검호전: 무사시 로드
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:33.17,TitleOP,en,0,0,90,,{\an8\fs32}Karakuri Kengouden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:33.17,TitleOP,en,0,0,48,,Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.99,0:00:33.17,TitleOP,en,0,0,0,,{\fs24}(The Story of {\i1}Karakuri{\i0} Martial Artist: Road of Musashi)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:38.01,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,사내는 언제나 세계 한가운데서
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:38.01,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A man always dreams of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.78,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,제일 강해질 날을
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.78,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,in the center of the world to become
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:44.65,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,아! 아! 꿈꿔라
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:44.65,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,AH! AH! the strongest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:49.69,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,마음의 칼을 넓은 하늘로 번쩍 쳐들어
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:49.69,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the sword of your heart high to the wide sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:54.33,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,모험의 길의 막을 연다
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:54.33,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Raise the curtain to the road of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.88,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구국을 떠도는 검호
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:01:00.88,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A skilled swordsman roams on Jipangu State
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:06.54,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,그 이름은 카라쿠리인 무사시
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:06.54,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His name is Musashi, a Karakuri man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.98,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,격렬한 승부의 소리는
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.98,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.82,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,눈부신 인생
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.82,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes a life dazzle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:19.32,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,싸웠던 어제보다도 오늘 강해진다
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:19.32,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Battles of yesterdays make you stronger today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:25.50,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,무예! 이도류 무사시
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:25.50,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.42,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,내일은 빛난다
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.42,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will be glorious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.00,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,격렬한 승부의 소리는
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.00,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,The sound of fierce duels
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.50,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,눈부신 인생
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.50,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,makes a life dazzle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.61,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,싸우는 한껏 고요함과 함께
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:39.61,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight the utmost with the stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:45.85,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,무예! 이도류 무사시
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:45.85,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:51.06,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,미간이 반짝였다 무사시!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:51.06,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His eyes shined! Musashi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:06.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마음먹고 목숨을 걸어 천하의 검술의 달인 보쿠덴에 뭐가 어떻게 되든 제자로 해 달라고
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:06.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi has been asking Bokuden, the master Martial Artist of the century, to accept him as a pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마음에 새긴 무사시의 열의의 과실이 보여 길고 쓰라린 수련이 시작되었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:11.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,and his strong desire has finally got him to start a long and bitter training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:18.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴의 검의 극의를 배운 무사시는 살아남아 미야코 궁전에 간다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:18.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, having learned the extreme art of swords from Bokuden, Musashi lives and heads for Miyako palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:23.61,TitleEP,ko,0,0,80,,수도의 고조의 벤케이
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:23.61,TitleEP,en,0,0,80,,Benkei from Gojo in the Capital
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사무라이 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미야코 궁전까지 가? 타고 가는 거 어때?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you going to Miyako palace? Why not ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,말은 필요 없소.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:49.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't need a horse-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거절할 필요 없어. 저렴해!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,No need to refuse. It's cheap after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걷는 쪽이 다리가 건강해지니 괜찮소.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.66,0:02:55.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Walking is good for the health of my legs, so I'll pass-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 말 하지 말고!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 문제 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anything wrong-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오줌! 이거 잠깐만!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hold this for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저기, 잠깐!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,곤란해졌소...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lose-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,늦소...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,He's being late-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.02,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,90,,{\fad(300,0)}벤케이
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.02,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,90,,{\fad(300,0)}Benkei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 좋아 보이는 말이구려.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,He looks like a pretty nice horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,확실히 좋은 말이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,It surely is a good horse-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:39.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보면 볼수록 반하겠네. 미안하네만 잠시 타 보아도 괜찮겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:39.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,The more I look, more I fall in love. Let me try riding for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 짓이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당연하다! 가지고 싶은 건 가져가는 게 내 방식이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't you see? Taking what I want is my principle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,야! 멈추시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,말도둑!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Horse thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈추시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:58.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시원하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,I feel refreshed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 일이야? 괜찮아?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,What happened? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:11.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배, 배가 고파서 못 움직이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:11.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,I cannot move because my stomach is empty-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 말은 어쩌고?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,What about my horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저기...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.22,0:04:14.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:25.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네가 부주의한 거니까 네 잘못이야! 어쩔 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:25.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,You were careless so it's your fault! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,설마 말도둑이라고는 생각하지 않았소...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:29.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,I didn't think he would be a horse thief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시끄러워! 어쨌든 니 잘못이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's your fault anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐가 무슨 일이 있어도 꼭 변상해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:34.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, you must compensate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그... 그러겠소...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저기가 내 집이야.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,That is my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 따라와.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:53.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,혼자 사는 것이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:05.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do you live alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래. 불만이라도 있냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right. Any problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:12.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,문제는 없지만, 아버지나 형제나 없소?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:12.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Not really, but don't you have a dad or brother-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 건 아무래도 상관없어.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,That doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:18.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그보다! 미야코에서 일해서 정말 변상할 거지?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:18.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Anyway! Are you really going to compensate me by working in Miyako?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:22.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,물론이오! 무예가 제일이 될 내가 못 할 일은 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:22.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course! As the future number one Martial Artist, I can do anything-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무예가 제일?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Number one Martial Artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐가 이상하오?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's so funny-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:33.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아무것도 아냐. 미야코 궁전에 나쁜 놈도 많이 있으니까 조심해.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:33.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nothing. There are lots of bad people in Miyako palace, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:38.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걱정 마오. 그런 놈이 나타난다면 내가 처리해 보이겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:38.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If such guy appears, I'll take care of him-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐가 이상하오?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:43.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's so funny-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:48.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 목검를 든 제일의 무예가라니 들은 적도 없어!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:48.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,But, I never heard a number one Martial Artist with a wooden sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,확실히 그게 맞는 말이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,That is true-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안. 필요없는 말을 했구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't mean to make you feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:02.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검술의 심오한 경지를 향해 배워 익히면 목검으로 진검승부를 볼 수도 있는 것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:02.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,It isn't impossible to have a real match by learning the innermost secrets of the techniques of sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도... 역시 진검이 있으면 좋겠소...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:07.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still... I'd still like a real sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안, 미안, 웃어버렸다!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry, for laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇게 검이 갖고 싶어?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do you want a real sword that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그야 당연하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course I want-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 좋은 곳을 소개해 줄게!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then I know a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:17.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,따라와!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:17.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여, 여긴?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:30.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어제 여기에서 전투가 있었어.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:30.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,There was a fight yesterday here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 여기서 검을 주우라는 것이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:34.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to pick up a sword from here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아까 검을 갖고 싶다 했잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,But you said you wanted one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:43.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,업신여기지 마시오! 검은 무사의 혼! 어느 세계에 길거리에서 혼을 주워 쓰는 자가 있소이까!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:40.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't look down on me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! A sword is the spirit of Martial Artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where in the world is a Martial Artist who uses a found spirit-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마음에 들었어! 좋아, 너 마음에 들어!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good job! Great, I like your attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너라면 분명히 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 될 수 있을 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,You will definitely manage to be the number one Martial Artist of Jipangu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:56.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-그, 그렇소?\N-당연하지! 힘내라!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:56.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Do you really think so-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?\N-Of course! Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:58.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:07.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이곳은 미야코 궁전. 황실이 있는 이 마을은 화려함으로 가득 차 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:07.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is Miyako palace. Brilliance was filling this village where the Royal Household is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:14.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검을 손에 넣고, 잃은 말을 변상하기 위해 무사시는 일을 찾아 걸어다녔다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:14.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,To get a sword and compensate for the lost horse, Musashi walked around to get a job.
