Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아이 돌보는 일이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Babysitting-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,츠카하라 보쿠덴에게 직접 전수받은 이 내가 이걸 하기에는 꼴이 말이 아니오만...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:23.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even I know it is pathetic to do this, after learning from Tsukahara Bokuden-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐든 하겠다는 정신은 바뀌지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am desperate enough-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,착하지! 착하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아... 보람없소...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,How fruitless-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저건!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,That must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:49.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 안 돼! 이런 모습! 제일의 수치오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:49.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Not now! Being in this shape is the number one embarrassment-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,울지 마라...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저 자... 무사시 닮았군.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,That man looks like Musashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,끈질기오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,So persistent-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이게! 이렇게 되어야 한다면!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bastard! If you're not going to stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정체를 보여라!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:30.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니잖아.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:30.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,He isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당연하지.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시가 아기 돌보는 일 따위를 하고 있을 리가 없지.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,No way Musashi's babysitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,위험했소...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,So close-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,착한 아이들이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good babies-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋소! 이번엔 내 특기를 보여드리겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now! Time for my specialties-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이걸 어쩌오...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:11.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,What should I do-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,야! 잘도 내 아이들을 울렸겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! How dare you make my babies cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sorry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 아이들 돌보는 일은 내게는 맞지 않소...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Babysitting is definitely not for me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
