Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이것이오, 이것!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 아닌 듯 하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,...isn't it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:42.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주인님 나가신다! 청소는 무엇보다도 깨끗하게!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:42.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,The master will be checking out! Make this place as clean as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:48.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이렇게는 아가들 돌보는 일보다도 처참하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:48.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is even more miserable than babysitting-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,도와주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이래서는 또 모가지오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll be fired again like this-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 일을 잘 하지 못했다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:15.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi wasn't good at working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 하지를 못하고 있소...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm not doing well-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 형!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,켄타! 어라, 그 말은 어디서 구했소?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kenta! Hey, where did you get that horse-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일단 말 하나는 있어야 먹고 사니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,I need a horse to live, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,렌탈 말이야.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's a rented horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,렌탈 말? 빌렸소? 돈은?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Rented horse? Did you borrow-{\i1}dasu{\i0}? What about the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,있을까 말까 한 걸레까지 털어냈어.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,I had to sell even a rag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래서 나 한푼도 없어.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Because of that I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,언제 보상할 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:42.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,When are you going to compensate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다양한 일을 하고 있으니 곧이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:45.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm doing various jobs, so it won't take long-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꼭 갚아! 부탁해!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:48.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do pay back! I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠소! 밑고 맡기소!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,I know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Leave it to me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:04.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시의 아르바이트는 원하는 대로 잘 되어가지 않았다.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:04.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi's part time job wasn't going well as he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:11.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 무사시는 쭉 끈질기게 포기하지 않고 켄타의 말 변상을 위해,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:11.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,But in order to compensate Kenta's horse, Musashi was tenacious and never gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:19.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고 꿈에서도 보는 진검을 위해 밤낮 구분없이 다양한 일에 힘썼다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:19.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Also, he worked all day and night to get a real sword that he always see in his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배고프오...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,So hungry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니야, 참아야 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, I must endure-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨 요즘 무엇하며 살지 궁금하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wonder how's Otsuru doing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:40.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 이제 곧 진검을 사게 되오.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:40.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will buy a real sword soon enough-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:47.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,진검을 손에 넣으면 어떤 무예가에도 지지 않는 제일이 되는 날이 멀지 않소.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:47.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,When I get a real sword, the day of becoming the number one Martial Artist who never loses to others will get even closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇게 되면 꼭 맞이하러 가겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:50.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,And when I become one, I'll take you as a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,야! 무슨 짓이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:08.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 검을 손에 넣을 수 있을 것인가. 질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:08.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Will Musashi manage to put his hands on a real sword? Wait for the stormy latter half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:12.99,Eyecatch,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리 검호전 무사시 로드
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:12.99,Eyecatch,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri Kengouden: Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야! 드디어 다 모았소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:16.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah! I finally saved up enough-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이걸로 검도 구매하고 빚도 갚겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:20.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll buy a sword and repay him-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:24.79,Note,ko,0,0,0,,{\frz-22\fs48\pos(285,259)}도검집
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:24.79,NoteOnAnimeVert,ko,0,0,0,,{\frz-94\pos(441,338)}전문점
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:24.79,Note,en,0,0,0,,{\frz-22\fs48\pos(285,259)}SWORD STORE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:24.79,Note,en,0,0,0,,{\frz-94\pos(476,342)}SPECIALTY SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:24.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어서오세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:24.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 좋은 검이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is good sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:33.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오, 눈이 높으시군요.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:33.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, you have a discerning eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 검 얼마나 하오?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,How much does this cost-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,음... 이 정도이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,About this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,와, 저렴하오! 2문이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's really cheap! Only two {\i1}mon{\i0}s-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.65,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(4000문 = 16주 = 4분 = 1양)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.65,Note,en,0,0,0,,(4000 {\i1}mon{\i0} = 16 {\i1}shu{\i0} = 4 {\i1}bu{\i0} = 1 {\i1}ryo{\i0})
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,심한 농담을! 20양이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're joking! It's 20 {\i1}ryo{\i0}s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,20양?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,20 {\i1}ryo{\i0}s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라, 무리인가요?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is it too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니오. 검은 무사의 생명. 좋은 것이라면 아낌없이 돈을 쓰겠으나...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nope. A sword is the spirit of Martial Artist. I'd spend money unsparingly for a good sword, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,조금만 더 저렴한 것을 원하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'd like a cheaper one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 이건 어떤가요?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then how is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이거라면 깎아서 25분!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,With discount, it only costs 25 {\i1}bu{\i0}s!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이거라면 어때요? 1양 2분!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:04.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's this? 1 {\i1}ryo{\i0} 2 {\i1}bu{\i0}s!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:05.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아직아직!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:05.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,단돈 1양!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Just 1 {\i1}ryo{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좀만 더!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,A bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정 안 되겠으면 9부 어떱니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,If that doesn't work, how is 9 {\i1}bu{\i0}s?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다시 비싸졌잖소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't fall for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당신, 정말로 살 생각은 있어요?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you going to buy or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,물론이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:18.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이보다 저렴한 검은 없어요!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is the cheapest sword here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,단돈 3분!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,Only 3 {\i1}bu{\i0}s!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,2부 반 되오?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Can you make it 2 {\i1}bu{\i0}s and a half-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,드디어 손에 넣었소.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Finally I got one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,하늘이 되었소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,I've became the sky-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.87,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(도움 안 되는 손님을 보내고 좋은 손님을 바라는 의미에서 소금을 뿌림)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.87,Note,en,0,0,0,,(He throws salt in hope of keeping away bad customers and attracting good customers)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다시는 오지 마라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Never come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:47.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야! 진검은 확실히 무게가 다르오!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.91,0:13:47.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,A real sword weights differently-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왠지 갑자기 신분이 높아진 기분이 드오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:50.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,I feel like I just became a person of high rank-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 광택.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,What brilliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 녀석은 괜찮게 획득한 것이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,I got this fair and square-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 괜찮은 것 같소.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Looks like a pretty good one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저렴하게 구입했으니 켄타네 말 변상도 가능하겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:14.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,Since I got in a low price, I'll can pay for Kenta's horse too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,딱 충분하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right on the mark-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:21.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이게 있으면 코지로한테서 숨으며 아르바이트한 가치가 보이는 것이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:21.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,With this, I see the value of doing part-time jobs, hiding from Kojirō-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로! 각오하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:24.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 자이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:37.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,That guy-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 벤케이가 말도둑이었다는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,So you're saying Benkei was the horse thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,켄타, 그 사람 알고 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kenta, do you know that guy-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:52.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,하나, 둘... 아, 유명하고말고. 좋아! 이거면 됐어. 확실히 받았어.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:52.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,One, two... Yeah, he's famous. Good! This will do. Thank you for compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:57.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이제 말끔해졌소. 그건 그렇고, 벤케이에 대해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:57.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,I feel clear-headed-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. Anyway, about Benkei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:03.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 말도 안 되는 놈한테 걸렸구나. 나도 들은 바이지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:03.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah, you were trapped by an unthinkable bastard. I only heard about him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:14.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,녀석은 미야코 고조 다리 위에 홀연 나타나 다리를 건너는 사무라이를 노려 승부를 봐 이기면 칼을 빼앗는다고 해.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:08.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is said that he appears on the bridge of Gojo of Miyako,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:14.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,and he targets the samurais to have a match and take their swords as booty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지금까지 999명의 사무라이가 칼을 빼앗겼다고 해.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is told that 999 samurais lost their swords until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,대단한 녀석이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:24.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,That guy is something-dsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래서 이제 어쩔 거야, 너?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,So what are you gonna do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,도전해야지? 벤케이한테?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,A challenge? Against Benkei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 알고 있었소?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Di- did you already know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:36.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당연하지! 너니까 말야. 그만하라 하도 안 들을 거잖아.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:36.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Of course! It's you after all. You're not going to stop even if I stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇게 대단한 놈이라면 상대로서 부족함이 없소.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,To know he's that dreadful, he is a perfect opponent for me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,반드시 이겨 보이겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:45.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:50.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}당장 일어날 일이구나. 뭐, 벤케이는 상대를 죽이진 않으니까 괜찮나?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:50.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's doing this right now... It shouldn't be harmful since Benkei doesn't kill his opponent, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:10.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벤케이! 연속 도검 강탈꾼 벤케이, 있소?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:10.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Benkei! Serial sword robber Benkei, are you there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:16.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무예가 제일에 한 발 가까워진 미야모토 마을의 무사시가 상대해 주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:16.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi from Miyamoto village has just taken another step to the number one Martial Artist, and he will face you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,승부볼 테니 나오시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come out and have a match-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,없는 것이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is nobody here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안 나올 것이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to come out-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:31.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 이 무사시가 두렵다는 것으로 받아들이겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:31.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then I'll take that as you fear me, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말 입만 살아가지고..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,He's all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,싸우지 않고 이겼소.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won without fighting-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,깔보지 마라.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:47.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왜 이 몸이 도망쳐야만 하는 것인가? 멍청한 놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:47.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why do I have to run away? You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:51.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벤케이! 등장!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:51.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Benkei's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나오셨소, 벤케이! 무사시가 상대해 주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,You came out, Benkei! Musashi will face you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오, 너는 그 때 꼬맹이냐.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, you're that kid from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이? 검으로 모자라 말까지 빼앗는 것은 비겁하기 짝이 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! To steal not only swords but also horses, you're very cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠소? 전력으로 승부를 보겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it? Let's have a match to death-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:09.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,관둬라, 관둬! 오늘밤은 기념할 만한 천번째의 밤.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:09.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give it up and shoo! Today is the monumental thousandth night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 상대는 실력있는 거물로 정했다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:12.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,I decided the opponent to be an important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 얘야! 얼렁 비켜라!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now, get lost, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:23.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,닥치시오! 난 아이가 아니오! kensei 보쿠덴의 가르침을 받은 제일의 제자이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:23.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shut up! I am not a kid! I am the only pupil of Bokuden, the master Martial Artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,녀석, 꽤 하네!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,He's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:41.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떻소! 물러나지 않은 걸 후회하지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:41.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's this? Don't regret doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:51.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시끄러운 애새끼가!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:51.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a noisy kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,산 지 얼마 안 된 칼이...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:04.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,I bought this sword today and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:08.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,녀석, 싼 걸 샀구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:08.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,I guess he bought a cheap one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,마, 말도 안 돼...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,No... no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:15.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,설마 그 도검집이 나에게 무딘 검을...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:15.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,That sword store must have sold me a blunt sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벌써 여기까지군. 게임 오버다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see it's settled. Game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무엇보다도 나에게 없는 것을 가져갈 생각이니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,I was going to take the one I don't have after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이렇게 됐으면 삶든지 태우던지 맘대로 하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore even if you boil or set me on fire literally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,방해하지 마라! 얼렁 비켜라!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't interfere! Just get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:04.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔가?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:04.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 허리에 있는 것을 가져가겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will take what you have on your waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오? 이걸?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:15.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그쪽의 금 야태도, 참으로 나의 천 번째로 어울리는 것.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:15.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Your gold large war sword will be a perfect fit for the thousandth item of my collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,순순히 주지 않겠는가?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you obediently pass it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,싫다.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:23.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런가. 그렇다면... 얻어서 내 것으로 만들 때까지!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:23.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see. If then... we'll fight until I get that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:38.22,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,80,,{\fad(300,0)}우시와카
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:38.22,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,80,,{\fad(300,0)}Ushikawa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:38.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그대가 밤마다 고조의 다리를 더럽힌다 하는, 거대한 바보의 벤케이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:38.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see that you're the big idiot who brings disgrace upon the bridge of Gojo every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미야코를 휩쓰는 고얀놈, 내가 퇴치하겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll get rid of the scoundrel that rampages in Miyako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐시라?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,놀리지 마라!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:19:59.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 일이냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:19:59.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장... 웃기지 마라!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn... don't fool around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐야?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:04.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떻냐. 내가 어떻게든 원하는 대로 되던가?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's that? Did you manage to make me pass the sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 이까짓 걸로...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,져, 졌다. 제가 졌습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:49.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lost, as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:54.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오늘 밤의 장물, 더욱 수련해야겠구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:54.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Tonight's useless thing should train more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기, 기다려 주십시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일단 존함을!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Tell me your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 이름을 알아서 어쩔 생각인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:04.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:08.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아무쪼록 이 벤케이를 깨달음의 다리로 부탁드립니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:08.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,I beg of you, please lead Benkei to the bridge of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:12.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왜 졌는지 알기 전까지는 만족하지 못하는구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:12.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see that you will remain unsatisfied before knowing why you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:13.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:13.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 가르쳐 드리겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 우시와카.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Ushiwaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우시와카라 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,You may call me Ushiwaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우시와카라...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:22.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ushiwaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기, 기다려 주십시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:23.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:28.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제발! 부디! 벤케이를!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:28.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please! I beg of you! Have Benkei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:40.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미야코 궁전에 나쁜 사람 많다고 했잖아.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:40.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,I told you there are many bad people in Miyako palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 알고 있소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,I know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:47.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,힘내. 나도 혼자서 어떻게든 힘내며 살고 있으니까.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:47.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Get a grip. I'm trying my best alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나... 나...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:50.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벤케이에게 진 게 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,I didn't lose to Benkei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:59.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모든 건... 모든 건 이것 잘못이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:59.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everything... everything is the fault of this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:18.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 또 세상의 넓음을 miyomotte 체험하게 되었다. 그것을 알고 있는가, 아닌가?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:18.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi experienced the wideness of the world again ~ly. Does he know that or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:23.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나! 이런 일로 꺾일 무사시가 아니다! 가라! 나아가라, 무사시여!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:23.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,But! Musashi isn't going to be discouraged because of such things. Go! Advance, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그것이 사내의 길이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:26.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,That is the road of man to stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:44.66,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,허공의 주머니에 달이
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:44.66,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.91,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,뛰어넘어가는 일도 있어
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.91,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of the empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.29,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,큰 소리로 웃으면
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.29,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.92,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,내일에는 아침이 와
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.92,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,a morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:58.26,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,잃는 것 따위는 아무것도 아니야
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:58.26,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't care too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.84,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,계속 해나가! 앞으로 가!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.26,0:23:01.84,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep doing! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.26,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,맨손은 강해
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.26,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:14.36,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.68,0:23:14.36,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:22.41,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,인생 그런 거야! 기회가 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:22.41,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:27.12,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,꼬리를 흔들며 쫒아와!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:27.12,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:38.05,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:38.05,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:46.51,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,미래도 그런 거야! 내일이 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:46.51,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how future also is! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:52.35,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,양손을 벌리고 웃고 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.76,0:23:52.35,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:11.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,요시오카 도장의 젊은 선생, 세쥬로를 쓰러뜨린 나는 제자들에게 쫒기는 신세에.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:11.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am being chased by pupils, after taking down a young teacher of Yoshioka Dōjō.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 때 구해준 분은 료마 씨.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,At that moment, Ryoma appeared and saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:17.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 이 사람, 달아나는 것도 훌륭한 병법의 하나라고 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.50,0:24:17.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,This person says that running away is one of the superb tactics-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:21.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 유연한 무예가는 처음 만나오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.77,0:24:21.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,I never met such easygoing Martial Artist-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:24.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음 이야기! 료마는 혼자 바람 속에
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:24.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! Ryoma is Alone in the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.54,0:24:27.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 활약을 보시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.54,0:24:27.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Be sure to check out the stormy action-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.35,NoteOnAnime,ko,60,0,60,,{\an7}다음 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.35,TitleEP,ko,0,0,70,,료마는 혼자 바람 속에
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.35,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}기대하세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.35,NoteOnAnime,en,60,0,60,,{\an7}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.35,TitleEP,en,0,0,80,,Ryoma is Alone in the Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.35,0:24:31.35,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!
